Profiles
Marriott
 



Richard Edwin and Nancy Peery Marriott








Joined the Giving Pledge: 12/10/2013 - Read the Letter

Estimated Net Worth: 
					$1.2 billion
				
Forbes Rank: #273
Industry: Hotels and resorts

Born: 

							Nancy Peery Marriott - Information not available
										Richard Marriott - 1939
						


Residence: 

								    Potomac,			    			    			        MD			    			    			


Richard Marriot runs Host Hotels & Resorts, the world's largest hotel-focused real estate investment trust, spun off in 1993 from the larger family-run Marriott International, founded by his father J.W. "Bill" Marriott in 1956. Nancy Peery Marriott is president of the Nancy Peery Marriott Foundation and is active among several national public-service organizations. She is an accomplished lyric soprano, having performed throughout the United States. 

